-03-22T19:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每一個人都唔同</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟<span style=\"color: red;\">你地</span>每一個人為咗乜嘢而生存？</blockquote><br />\nok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該係為左理解咩係生命 同埋身邊既人</blockquote><br />\n絲打應該係鍾意享受生命個啲人嚟？"},{"pid":"304f360cfef36f7084189840d9f4be708f319c06","tid":166031,"uid":8514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要有啖好食 就可以生存落去"},{"pid":"e4b6eb56b13a858921a6f4f2f4210e7c35b57a00","tid":166031,"uid":33363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每一個人都唔同</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟<span style=\"color: red;\">你地</span>每一個人為咗乜嘢而生存？</blockquote><br />\nok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該係為左理解咩係生命 同埋身邊既人</blockquote><br />\n絲打應該係鍾意享受生命個啲人嚟？</blockquote><br />\n算係掛 對生活品質有一定要求 但又唔會話一定要食好住好果隻？<br />\n想理解比較係因為自己曾經好唔開心 甚至到依家都係冇目標 所以想知何謂生命 搵存在既意義"},{"pid":"840c2464ea29afe938c01770b6a0b06dd2c6132d","tid":166031,"uid":32666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:12:34.000Z","msg":"為自己<br />\n因為人不為己 天誅地滅 <br />\n唔為自己就一早死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e642d293c8b4bc6f39b2bf3ad793f85a4ee612da","tid":166031,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔知為乜<br />\n所謂目標理想都係人自己定架姐"},{"pid":"fce927e73a77c413f83d43133153cd589c9ff55c","tid":166031,"uid":90976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:19:24.000Z","msg":"為左另一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩決定左唔再中意男神 覺得唔再中意佢既自己唔係自己咁"},{"pid":"509b